TITLE: Hard Rule Visual Step Is Not Execution
STATEMENT: >>>
After the six executable steps complete, the current UI may advance the sidebar/status display through Hard Rule Integration and LLM-Ready Context labels.

That visual progression shall not be interpreted as execution of a global Hard Rule engine or a final external model call.
<<<
