  VALUE: GHOST-SP-PROJECTION-ROOT

[REQUIREMENT]
UID: GHOST-SP-PROJECTION-HARD-RULE-POSTPONED
STATUS: Draft
TITLE: Global Hard Rule Integration Postponed
STATEMENT: >>>
Global Hard Rule integration shall remain disabled and planned for later in the current runtime baseline.

Per-agent static JSON instructions named Hard Rules shall not be confused with the future global Hard Rules capability.
<<<
RELATIONS:
- TYPE: Parent
  VALUE: GHOST-SP-PROJECTION-ROOT

[REQUIREMENT]
UID: GHOST-SP-PROJECTION-FUTURE-SEND-SAME-ASSEMBLY
STATUS: Draft
TITLE: Future Send Uses Authoritative Assembly
STATEMENT: >>>
The approved future direction is that the actual model-call/send boundary shall consume the same authoritative deterministic prompt assembly represented to the user, so final-send content does not silently diverge from the inspectable engineered prompt.
<<<
RELATIONS:
- TYPE: Parent
  VALUE: GHOST-SP-PROJECTION-ROOT

[REQUIREMENT]
UID: GHOST-SP-PROJECTION-FUTURE-NO-API-INVENTION
STATUS: Draft
