STATEMENT: >>>
This document shall not invent the future model-provider API, model-selection contract, streaming behavior, response-capture behavior, retry policy, or failure semantics before those decisions are implemented or explicitly approved.
<<<
RELATIONS:
- TYPE: Parent
  VALUE: GHOST-SP-PROJECTION-ROOT

