[[SECTION]]
TITLE: 12. Failure and Integrity Requirements

[REQUIREMENT]
UID: GHOST-SP-PROJECTION-NO-MISSING-CONTEXT-FABRICATION
STATUS: Draft
TITLE: Missing Context Omission
STATEMENT: >>>
Projection shall omit empty Memory Context, empty S_CTX_MD, absent ActiveBrief content, and absent attachment content rather than invent replacements.
<<<
RELATIONS:
- TYPE: Parent
  VALUE: GHOST-SP-PROJECTION-ROOT

[REQUIREMENT]
UID: GHOST-SP-PROJECTION-NO-RAW-MEMORY-LEAK
STATUS: Draft
TITLE: No Default Raw Memory Leakage
STATEMENT: >>>
Normal prompt_ready rendering shall not expose raw memory episodes, raw semantic-memory chunks, or memory debug Markdown merely because they exist in MemoryContextPack or extras.
<<<
RELATIONS:
- TYPE: Parent
  VALUE: GHOST-SP-PROJECTION-ROOT

[REQUIREMENT]
