STATEMENT: >>>
Raw retrieved document text shown in the engineered prompt shall use the current sanitization path so source headings and structural markers do not compete with the outer SuperPrompt structure.
<<<
RELATIONS:
- TYPE: Parent
  VALUE: GHOST-SP-PROJECTION-ROOT

[REQUIREMENT]
UID: GHOST-SP-PROJECTION-NO-DURABLE-MUTATION
